snippet.title: Raymond Cripps
snippet.description:
Creator, developing Project Feline, an anime-style parkour adventure!

If you've ever wanted to learn about how video games are made, then this is the channel for you! Join me on my journey to create my dream game. Through my ongoing Project Feline Devlog series, I document the my development process towards creating a commercial video game entirely on my own from start to finish!

https://www.projectfeline.com
